==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Clancular
<hw>Clan"cu*lar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>clancularius</ets> , from <ets>clanculum</ets> secretly, adv. dim.
of <ets>clam</ets> secretly.]</ety> <def>Conducted with secrecy;
clandestine; concealed.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Not close and <qex>clancular</qex>, but frank and open.</q>
<rj><qau>Barrow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Clancularly</ent>⟦br⟧
